values: Well basically what ive been doin lately is getting into what HOPEFULLY ill end up doing sooner in later in life, which is digital media design. Ive already been looking up courses, and in school they taught me about stuff like that and ive been getting really into it. So basically ive been mixin it up with skateboarding and bringing them both together. And Chris, a long time ago we had this idea. it never really happend though cuz we were to busy to put it up. So i put my thoughts to work..and with the help of some of my other friends this should be very interesting a fun. *Note* This isnt a SERIOUS SERIOUS thing, just something localy around here, and give people a chance to see something new. But we'll see in the future what develops out of it.
Did someone say RRILM?!? This is what you get when you have a slumber party....And your HIGH on skateboarding.....Good day people.

Well, it has started to rain.  I wasn't really able to skateboard today anyways. Exhausted, sore.  So for now i'll probly end up eatind, and playing with photoshop and take pictures.  So im reading my old journal, and I notice alot of people getting angry..haha, girls will be girls.  So much tension between so many people.  This is my new one.  And earlier today I finally made a decision to stay at Madison and not attend a different school like southwest prep or ace.  I'll do what I can to graduate.  This weekend ill be looking for a job, and go looking for a car.  Need to stop being in my lazy moods. 


"I have plenty of time to rest when im dead...Until then  I will skate night and day...rain or shine..."     Von
